well yesterday i went to surf camp with some of my friends.....i had fun it was pretty cool...one of my best friends is having trouble with her boyfriend who i happened to c at surf camp...well he told me all this stuff and well he didnt really tell me a whole lot...linz did...but ya...shese really depressed so this is wut i have to say:

i just got back 
from a trip around the world
to find that u and ur boyfriend
had been hurled down this unsure path,
and who knows where u will end up 
but i hope u guys will stay friends and
maybe more than that but i say
im sorry if u didnt make it together
i hope ur life will turn around so u
can see the sun before it sents down on u,
pray to god and ask him wut to do
and if its not what u wanted 
remember its good for u.....
im back frommy trip and im as tired as can be
im prayin that u and him will be better and youll see
that this path that ur on will brighten up
and lighten up..so dont worry..everything is in
Gods hands.
 
 ok that was for my friend nat...i hope u like it but if u dont sry!!!! luv u guys hope everything turns out ok!!

r these live journals supposed to b 4 ur feelings? well i guess thats how im gonna use mine..if u guys dont mind...well i hope all goes well for me this summer....i mean my weekly weather report would be....cloudy with some sunshine......but luckly no thunderstorms yet..hehehe...well i hope i have fun this week....heres a little sumthin hope u enjoy:
   
i hope im not to late
to tell u how i feel;
cuz if i am wut will i do
to get me back to you?
and if i get my chance to tell u how i feel
this is wut i would say..
im sorry i hurt u 
im sorry i let u down
im sorry i was diffuclt to you...
but i must confess this one thing
before i go..and thats
to tell you
that i luv u 
that i'll miss you for eternity
im sorry im a little late 
to tell u this big news
but to me and hopefully to u
all that matters is that..
i luv u
 
  07/20/04
  well hope u guys all like it.....buh bye!
